# 5. Scheduler Service

Responsible for execution decisions.

```go id="sbb0rb"
type Scheduler interface {

    SubmitTask(ctx context.Context, cmd SubmitTaskCommand) (SubmitTaskResult, error)

    DispatchTask(ctx context.Context, cmd DispatchTaskCommand) (DispatchTaskResult, error)

    ReserveResources(ctx context.Context, cmd ReserveResourcesCommand) (ReserveResourcesResult, error)

    ReleaseResources(ctx context.Context, cmd ReleaseResourcesCommand) (ReleaseResourcesResult, error)

    ListQueue(ctx context.Context, cmd ListQueueCommand) (ListQueueResult, error)
}
```

The Scheduler owns execution.

